data.title: 2008) – Find a Grave Gedenkstätte
data.meta_description: Frank G. Castillo, 64, of Bartlett died Monday, March 24, 2008 at Scott & White Hospital in Temple, Texas. Visitation will be 6-8 PM, with Rosary recited at 7 PM, on Wednesday, March 26, 2008 at Providence Funeral Home Chapel in Taylor.
